rome is an important centre for music it hosts the  accademia nazionale di santa cecilia  founded in 1585 for which new concert halls have been built in the new  parco della musica  one of the largest musical venues in the world rome also has an  opera house  the  teatro dellopera di roma  as well as several minor musical institutions the city also played host to the  eurovision song contest 1991  and the  mtv europe music awards 2004
